column2: SELECT TOP # artist.Name, artist.ArtistId, COUNT (Track.AlbumId) AS Num_tracks, SUM (Track.UnitPrice) As Price FROM chinook.Album album INNER JOIN chinook.Track track ON album.AlbumId = track.AlbumId INNER JOIN chinook.Artist artist ON album.ArtistId = artist.ArtistId GROUP BY artist.Name, album.AlbumId ORDER BY SUM (Track.UnitPrice) DESC
